snippet.title: ED SHEERAN | CHICKEN SHOP DATE
snippet.description:
Amelia meets Ed Sheeran at Sam’s Chicken for a date.

Created and Written by Amelia Dimoldenberg.
Co-Writer: Ania Magliano

Director: Amelia Dimoldenberg
Producer: Georgie Goadsby
Executive Producer: Zoe Morris

Cam A: Jack Ayers
Cam B: Edie Amos
Sound Op: Jordan Tewskbury

Editor: Joe Bolger
Conform: Matt Easy  

Colourist: Fraser Twitchett @ Okay Studio
Sound Design/Mix: Mark Duckett @ Bounce

Animation by Naomi Anderson-Subryan
Social Media: Jade Whiteley & Zoe Morris

Thank you to Sam’s Chicken in Queen’s Park, W9!

Ed Sheeran’s song ‘Shivers’ is available here - https://es.lnk.to/ShiversMI/itunes’
